## Agent behavior

When starting a new vertical slice or phase:

- Read the matching phase section in the checklist first.
- Cite which gates were satisfied in the PR summary.
- If a gate cannot be met yet, document the gap and do not mark the phase complete.

Privacy rules in [docs/system/privacy-and-identity.md](../../docs/system/privacy-and-identity.md) are security requirements — not optional UX.
